// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0125 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a93732d9-42fd-5fcf-a397-b8102d41d79f

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*almalinux:8*" or process.executable like~ "*almalinux:9*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:8*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:9*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
